searchParameters.q: how much is a 1986 penny worth

answerBox.snippet: A 1986 no-mint mark penny is worth only $0.05 and $0.10 in circulated condition. Even uncirculated coins in mint state are not worth much and will typically bring in $2 to $8. As a general rule, you shouldn't expect a premium from a 1986 Lincoln penny.
